    {
      "id": "PopularPost328732",
      "post_content": "I think he's a LITTLE better than everyone's giving him credit for. [Security Blockade](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Security Blockade) was pretty solid in RTR limited, and this basically provides the same effect. Granted, it's on a 1/1 goon and doesn't give you a populatable 2/2 Vigilant Knight, but this also costs 2 less mana and can be used even when the opponent isn't damaging you, for what it's worth. I know, I know, \"LIFEGAIN IZ BADD!\" and yes, there are cards that do it way better, but I've seen my fair share of games (especially in limited) where that 1 life was the difference in the match.",
      "posted_by": "BilliamQ",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost328732\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">I think he's a LITTLE better than everyone's giving him credit for. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Security Blockade\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Security Blockade\">Security Blockade</a> was pretty solid in RTR limited, and this basically provides the same effect. Granted, it's on a 1/1 goon and doesn't give you a populatable 2/2 Vigilant Knight, but this also costs 2 less mana and can be used even when the opponent isn't damaging you, for what it's worth. I know, I know, \"LIFEGAIN IZ BADD!\" and yes, there are cards that do it way better, but I've seen my fair share of games (especially in limited) where that 1 life was the difference in the match.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '328732'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy36483\">BilliamQ</span>\r\n                                (7/12/2013 8:26:54 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularP